{"tid":1915558,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Christian Bale 將出演《Thor 4》反派","createTime":"2020-03-08T09:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T04:35:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"681c5ee6b7ea553e3d1db98edf5ca53754c265d3","tid":1915558,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"《Dark Knight》喺咁多年後都彼認為係最成功嘅Batman，除咗導演路蘭嘅功力，Christian Bale嘅演技當然係功不可沒。而如果你以為以後都冇機會見到Christian Bale出演超級英雄片，咁就錯啦！因為最新消息已經確認，Christian Bale會於Marvel嘅《Thor4》飾演反派！<br />\n<br />\n喺Thor系列中飾演女武神(Valkyrie)嘅Tessa Thompson，近日接受紅地毯訪問時透露Christian Bale將會加盟Thor第四集，《Thor: Love and Thunder》並飾演反派，但佢就冇講明反派角色究竟係邊一個。而Fans們就估計Christian Bale嘅角色係「Galactus」，最早出現於《Fantastic Four》中，Marvel世界五大神之一，原著實力比Thanos更高，如果消息屬實，相信Christian Bale會成為Marvel宇宙將來嘅重要一員。<br />\n<br />\n預計2021年11月上映嘅Thor第四集《Thor: Love and Thunder》，除咗有Tessa Thompson及Chris Hemsworth回歸，上集導演兼憑《Jojo Rabbit》奪得金像獎最佳改編劇本嘅Taika Waititi亦會繼續執導，而於前兩集飾演Jane Foster的Natalie Portman亦會回歸，而根據原著劇情，Jane Foster將會接過雷神之槌，成為新一代Thor。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/hobby/23309?fbclid=IwAR0JuAfpIXi9ViHFIIAD7WB966oSdriqKvumycI7LOdz1c2qUxnQSrc1d9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fhobby%2F23309%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0JuAfpIXi9ViHFIIAD7WB966oSdriqKvumycI7LOdz1c2qUxnQSrc1d9s&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw3O%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=76fc94f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/hobby/23309?fbclid=IwAR0JuAfpIXi9ViHFIIAD7WB966oSdriqKvumycI7LOdz1c2qUxnQSrc1d9s</a>"},{"pid":"ceaf1ea62c803a10a04813839a5276174c6998a3","tid":1915558,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:59:41.000Z","msg":"下 咪搞啦撲乖&hellip;😥"},{"pid":"114228fea2b0ed00b7db6602af46d0e1975be53f","tid":1915558,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"Natalie 真係做女雷神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=